---
title: Saucy Turkey Tacos with Salsa Rice and Feta
description: Get ready for your new go-to Taco Night recipe, because these saucy handhelds are sure to be a hit! They're jam-packed with spices, served with seasoned salsa rice and topped off with creamy feta cheese.
